TopicTitle: Symmetry places one out of 4 engines upside down

Articles.Content:
During flight I noticed one of my 4 symmetric engines was upside down. When I went back to the VAB it was inverted there as well. I removed the part and all 4 came off. Re-attached and everything was right-side up. Can not reproduce.
